<p style="text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;"><em><img title="Zakharov_NB.jpg" src="uploads/images/Speakers_foto/Zakharov_NB.jpg" alt="Zakharov_NB.jpg" width="90" height="110" /></em></p>
